Third Department,

November, 1939.

(November 1, 1939.) In the Matter of the Claim of Jerry Cohen, Appellant, against S. Blechman & Sons, Employer, and State Insurance Fund, Respondent. State Industrial Board, Respondent.

Motion for permission to present appeal on typewritten record granted. Present — Hill, P. J., Crapser, Bliss, Sehenek and Foster, JJ.
